description:
Pinjra | 1972 | V.Shantaram's Immortal Marathi Classic | Phantom

Pinjra aka &quot;The Cage&quot; is one of greatest masterpiece by master of Cinema, V Shantaram. Made in 70s it explores a complex web love, sex and relationships. Why and how people lose the respect in their own eyes, of choices or lack of choices people make in their life.

Its a must watch movie for anyone who wants to explore complex web love , life and life with respect and love with meaning and how all of this can be turned upside down by a very basic human urge of sex. A masterpiece &amp; classical Greek tragedy.

All the songs of Pinjra are classics of Marathi Cinema:

1 ..Aali Thumkat Naar Lachkat..Vishnu Waghmare &quot; Waghya&quot;
2 ..Chhabidar Chhabi Mi Toryat Ubhi..Usha Mangeshkar
3 ..De Re Kanha Choli Un Lugdi..Usha Mangeshkar
4 ..Disla Ga Bai Disla..Lata Mangeshkar
5 ..Tumhawar Keli Mi Marji Bahal..Usha Mangeshkar
6 ..Kashi Nashibana Thatta Aaj Mandli..Sudhir Phadke
7 ..Mala Lagli Kunachi Uchaki..Usha Mangeshkar
8 ..Naka Todu Pavna Jara Thamba..Usha Mangeshkar
9 ..Ishqachi Ingli Dasli..Usha Mangeshkar

Awards:
1973 - National Film Award for Best Feature Film in Marathi

